    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "On further investigation, it appears to be related to rocksdb 7.9.2 which was released as part of teku 23.2.0.\n\nThe peers appearing to fix the problem may have been due to reduced concurrency...\n\nTo resolve this issue, reverted to 7.7.3 and the freezing has stopped.\n\nThe PR making this change was #6930. It was not in 23.3.0, will be in the next release.",
